'From Squeak3.7alpha of 11 September 2003 [latest update: #5707] on 15 February 2004 at 12:42:39 pm'!"Change Set:		FixObsoletePrefs-nkDate:			15 February 2004Author:			Ned KonzEvery time we change the Preferences class, we hold onto the old versions in individual preferences.This CS repairs existing Preferences to point to the current Preferences class."| obsoletePrefs |Smalltalk garbageCollect.obsoletePrefs _Preference allSubInstances select: [ :ea | | ci |	ci _ (ea instVarNamed: 'changeInformee').	ci isBehavior and: [ ci isObsolete ] ].obsoletePrefs do: [ :pref |	| ci |	ci _ (pref instVarNamed: 'changeInformee').	pref instVarNamed: 'changeInformee' put: (Smalltalk at: ci name ifAbsent: []) ].Behavior flushObsoleteSubclasses.!